00:19:32,490 --> 00:19:34,220
You hear that?

264
00:19:39,130 --> 00:19:42,200
I'm guessing everybody knows about the competition.

265
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:46,590
Everyone's GPA is above 3.9, that why I recommended you to compete.

266
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:48,550
I called everyone over today,

267
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:52,980
