268
00:19:54,100 --> 00:19:58,420
So whether you've started preparing or not, note that the time is running out. Understand?

269
00:19:59,990 --> 00:20:02,540
All right, Go and get ready.

270
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,810
Thank you, Teacher.

271
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:11,200
Liang Younian, wait a moment. Come, have a seat.

272
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:16,980
Why is Lin Kaituo not here?

273
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:21,520
My cousin got hurt, and he took her to the infirmary.

274
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:24,630
- Then pass the message onto him when you see him.
- All right.

275
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:27,690
Liang Younain.

276
00:20:27,690 --> 00:20:29,230
Professor Wu.

277
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:31,940
Professor Lin said that you were participating in the competition, too.

278
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:33,100
Yes.

279
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:36,140
Chen Hui also participated in the competition that time.

280
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:39,390
And she got a place, too. It was first place.

281
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:41,660
Yes, of course.

282
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,090
You can do it just like your mom, too.

283
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:45,750
Thank you, Professor.

284
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:49,570
Haicheng University

285
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:18,730
I've selected you from so many and been training you so hard

286
00:21:18,730 --> 00:21:20,560
And you give me this in return.

287
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:23,190
Are you not happy with me?

288
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:27,570
Teacher, why don't you get the third substitute?

289
00:21:27,570 --> 00:21:29,670
How am I going to get her back? I've eliminated her.

290
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:32,140
Do you want me to look shameless?

291
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,400
Stop acting now.

292
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,560
Look how worried Teacher is.

293
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:39,790
No way, Lin Kaitou is finally taking care of me.

294
00:21:39,790 --> 00:21:42,700
I have to act this way until the end.

295
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:45,540
Teacher, I'll just need to rest for a few days and I'll be fine.

296
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,990
- After that, I'll...
- It's fine, it's fine.

297
00:21:47,990 --> 00:21:49,630
Go and rest.

298
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:57,510
Teacher, Miaomiao wants to throw the baton.

299
00:22:00,170 --> 00:22:02,070
She is talented and learns fast.

300
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:05,540
Also, she can catch things fast, accurately and steadily.

301
00:22:06,850 --> 00:22:08,450
It's you then.

302
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:22,300
Throw. Throw. Throw it up.

303
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:29,130
Teacher, I really can't do it.

304
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:33,420
It's fine. Just throw it up higher.

305
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:42,690
Senior. Are you all right?

306
00:22:42,690 --> 00:22:44,180
Why did you hit me?

307
00:22:44,180 --> 00:22:46,510
I didn't mean to.

308
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:49,000
Let me take a look.
 [Architecture Department]

309
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,740
Y-You squat down.

310
00:22:50,740 --> 00:22:53,100
Let me see if your head is all right.

311
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:59,400
It's a little red. I'm sorry.

312
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:39,400
Are you all right?

313
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,200
- I'm all right.
- Good.

314
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:46,000
He's all right. Come practice now.

315
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,000
Hurry up.

316
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,400
I'm going back to the model room.

317
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:56,200
Throw it up. Higher!

318
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,100
Hurry! Toss it up!

319
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:28,200
Miaomiao! Higher, please!

320
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:35,000
One more time! Hurry up! Higher!

321
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:56,200
Xiaoyue. You're finally here.

322
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:58,400
Are you here to draw?

323
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:01,000
I'm here to get something. I've got to go now.

324
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,700
Hey...

325
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:20,700
Liang Younaian, are you laughing at me?

326
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,000
I didn't say anything.

327
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,100
Your eyes are speaking.

328
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:28,600
Did they say that...

329
00:25:28,600 --> 00:25:31,900
You are a bit of a scaredy-cat when you fall for someone?

330
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,990
Fine, you're the only one that's not a scaredy-cat.

331
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:38,000
I think there's something wrong with you.

332
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:39,460
You tear drawings one after another.

333
00:25:39,460 --> 00:25:41,600
Open windows when the air conditioner is on.

334
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:43,700
Don't you know how to be environmentally friendly?

335
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:54,000
This... toss it upward.

336
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,800
Higher. Toss it.

337
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:06,600
You have the nerves to tease me for being a scaredy-cat.

338
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:12,700
Unlike someone who doesn't even know he's in love.

339
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:16,400
Wh-What... What are you talking about?

340
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:18,400
What am I talking about?

341
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:21,000
Think about it yourself.

342
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:25,900
Do you really treat Xia Miaomiao as a younger sister?

343
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:54,700
Teacher, it hurts.

344
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:56,070
That's right then.

345
00:26:56,070 --> 00:26:57,800
Just get hurt a few more times, you'll get it then.

346
00:26:57,800 --> 00:26:59,400
Keep it up!

347
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:12,000
Teacher!

348
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:15,700
Just getting hurt a few more times and it'll be fine.

349
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:24,200
Keep practicing. I'll find someone to bring you food.

350
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:26,200
Don't give up.

351
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:30,400
Is it going to be all night training?

352
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:55,800
Kaituo, you're here.

353
00:27:57,500 --> 00:28:00,200
Your injury is serious to this extent?

354
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:06,600
Didn't the doctor say it is not necessary to dress it?

355
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:10,200
I got it looked again by another doctor,

356
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:14,000
and he said it is necessary to dress the wound as it was very serious.

357
00:28:17,100 --> 00:28:19,000
Let's go.

358
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,400
Aren't you going to carry me?

359
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:26,000
Do you believe that I'm going back to work on my design now?

360
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:30,400
All right. At least help me to carry something.

361
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:45,400
Slowly.

362
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:56,200
Miaomiao, what are you doing?

363
00:28:56,200 --> 00:29:00,000
I didn't even catch the baton once.

364
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:09,600
It's for you.

365
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:11,400
Can't you just talk nicely?

366
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:14,000
I'm sorry.

367
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:18,100
Kaituo, Miaomiao is going to have lunch soon. Can you help her find the baton?

368
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:22,000
No. I can find it myself.

369
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:26,800
You eat, I'll go.

370
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,200
I'm starving.

371
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,400
How long is this wound dressing going to last?

372
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:44,000
I don't know either, but it works really well.

373
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:48,700
Look. I asked him to find the baton for you, and he listened to me.

374
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:52,300
What do you like about him? Look at the way he runs.

375
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:56,400
I was wrong.

376
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,800
- It's delicious, right?
- Yes.

377
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:02,600
Delicious! Xinxin is the best.

378
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:07,790
This is so light. Is it that hard to do?

379
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:09,600
I can get it just by watching.

380
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,000
Show us if you can.

381
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:13,200
- Sure.
- Wow!

382
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,200
It looks so cool.

383
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:16,000
It hasn't even started yet.

384
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:39,600
Not bad. Not bad. Better than Miaomiao.

385
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,200
I just miscalculated the parabola.

386
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:46,200
Hold on. Let me recalculate the parabola.

387
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:47,400
Yes.

388
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,760
Kaituo is right.

389
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:51,400
This is just a matter of dynamics.

390
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:54,400
Why don't you say it's about gravity?

391
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:56,310
I'm begging both of you, go and do whatever you should be doing.

392
00:30:56,310 --> 00:30:58,200
Don't interrupt my training here.

393
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,600
Wait.

394
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:07,600
Just go. Okay.

395
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:09,400
I'll try again.

396
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:11,600
Just hurry and leave.

397
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:17,200
If you're still not going to ask him to leave, I'll tell him that your leg is actually fine.

398
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:22,600
Kaituo. Oh, my. Let's go.

399
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:26,600
Teacher Jia is coming back soon.

400
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:29,400
- Let's go.
- Okay. Okay.

401
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,500
Be careful.

402
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:42,000
My goodness.

403
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:04,200
How to tell if you like someone.

404
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:09,400
At any time, you'll always want to glance at places where she appears.

405
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:13,000
Why am I so unlucky?

406
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:18,500
I wish I were taller.

407
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:25,500
Can someone help me?

408
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:28,000
I can.

409
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:33,800
S... Senior.

410
00:34:34,790 --> 00:34:37,420
Why are you here?

411
00:34:39,660 --> 00:34:41,360
I was just passing by.

412
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:44,400
Passing by?

413
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:46,900
Are you trying to take that down?

414
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:53,000
Let me help you.

415
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:10,600
♫ Can you see my heart ♫

416
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:13,200
♫ Can you read my mind ♫

417
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:19,800
♫ Live inside my eyes, tell me words of love tenderly ♫

418
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:25,400
♫ I want you by my side, always watching over ♫

419
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:29,700
♫ My heart... ♫

420
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:41,400
♫ My heart restlessly beats whenever I see you  ♫

421
00:35:46,200 --> 00:35:48,400
What is that sound?

422
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:54,200
Just now.

423
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:58,600
Don't be afraid. I'll go and check.

424
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:09,700
Hello, you're so cute.

425
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:22,470
It's so cute.

426
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:32,500
Senior, how can someone be stone-hearted as to abandon such a cute puppy?

427
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:36,200
True.

428
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:42,000
It's late right now. I'll have to take it back to the dorm with me.

429
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:59,000
I'm sorry about that just earlier.

430
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:02,000
How about you take it off and give it to me?

431
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:04,000
I'll wash it for you.

432
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,800
It is okay. I'll wash it myself.

433
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:09,000
I'm so worried right now.

434
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:11,800
I've been practicing all day to catch the baton,

435
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:14,100
but I still can't catch it.

436
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:17,000
You've indeed just been hitting your head.

437
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:20,000
How did you know that I kept hitting my head?

438
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:23,900
Wasn't I hit by you once today?

439
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,900
That is true.

440
00:37:29,010 --> 00:37:31,790
Let's go down and move around.

441
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:37,310
Unfortunately, pets aren't allowed on the campus.

442
00:37:37,310 --> 00:37:40,600
I need to find a good household to adopt you.

443
00:37:48,600 --> 00:37:51,100
You better come over here.

444
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:53,700
Little baby.

445
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:58,200
It's so cute.

446
00:37:58,200 --> 00:38:02,900
Look. Her bright eyes, they're like Kaitou's?

447
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:09,600
I know you've pretended to limp lately, and that relationship between you two has developed fast.

448
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:12,200
But you can't just lie in this way.

449
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:17,400
In my mind, Kaituo does indeed have bright eyes.

450
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:20,600
Xinxin, could you help me make a post

451
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:24,000
in the university forum to find someone to adopt this puppy?

452
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:26,600
Don't you want to raise it?

453
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:28,000
I...

454
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:32,200
Some people aren't letting her keep it.

455
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:35,400
Okay, then I'll help you and post it when I get back to my dorm.

456
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,850
When are you going to send it away?

457
00:38:36,850 --> 00:38:38,600
The room is full of people because of it.

458
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:40,400
It's so annoying.

459
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,680
I'm sorry.

460
00:38:41,680 --> 00:38:44,200
After I find someone to adopt it, I'll send it away.

461
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:47,600
Xia Miaomiao! Take a look at this yourself.

462
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:49,300
What's wrong?

463
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:55,400
I'm sorry, I'm sorry. I'll wash the table cloth for you in a bit.

464
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:59,200
Forget about "in a bit", I'm going to throw it out now.

465
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,200
No, don't.

466
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:03,200
Tang Mengfei, turn around.

467
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:06,000
What are you doing?!

468
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,000
Go ahead and throw it.

469
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:11,100
If you dare to do so, I'll record it and post it on the university forum.

470
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,600
And let everyone see how our university Belle bullies such a small animal?

471
00:39:12,600 --> 00:39:16,600
And let everyone see how our university Belle bullies such a small animal?

472
00:39:21,300 --> 00:39:23,400
Take it, take it.

473
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:27,600
Delete it now!

474
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,800
Okay, I'll delete it.

475
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:37,200
Look at what you've done.

476
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:39,600
- What happened?
- Well done.

477
00:39:44,600 --> 00:39:47,200
Where did this puppy come from? It's so cute.

478
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:49,000
I picked it up from somewhere, Senior Sister.

479
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,000
Look at it.

480
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:55,000
Architecture Department

481
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:05,100
I think the proportions of the swimming pool is a bit...

482
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,800
Look.

483
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:17,400
The location of the office area...

484
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:22,800
I'll talk to you later.

485
00:40:33,200 --> 00:40:35,000
Your food delivery.

486
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:41,820
I bought it for Liang Younain, and for you too in passing.

487
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:46,200
Am I right?

488
00:40:57,400 --> 00:41:00,000
Why are you still amending this drawing?

489
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:02,900
Then why do you keep coming to our classroom?

490
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:08,800
I've only been here a few times, but not as many times as you amended this column.

491
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:11,800
Get out. Don't bother me while I'm drawing.

492
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:16,200
No, I just don't understand. It's just a broken column, is it necessary to amend for so many times?

493
00:41:16,200 --> 00:41:18,200
- Right, Xiaoyue?
- Yes.

494
00:41:19,600 --> 00:41:20,800
What are you drawing?

495
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,600
It's a swimming pool.

496
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:24,800
Swimming pool?

497
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:28,900
I love swimming. Let me take a look how it's coming along.

498
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:32,400
My goodness. It looks so realistic..

499
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,530
It looks just like a real swimming pool.

500
00:41:34,530 --> 00:41:36,800
My god. I feel like going to swim there now.

501
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:37,800
Awesome.

502
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,200
Let me finish drawing first.

503
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,720
It's so much better than Liang Younians.

504
00:41:40,720 --> 00:41:42,200
It's really a good drawing.

505
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:44,800
Don't need to draw it again. You'll definitely get first place. [Chinese-Style Courtyard]

506
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:47,400
It's drawn so well.
[Chinese-Style Courtyard]

507
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:49,420
And she got a place, too.

508
00:41:49,420 --> 00:41:51,600
It was first place.

509
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:54,400
I will as well.

510
00:42:40,600 --> 00:42:42,800
Slowly, slowly.

511
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:50,400
Actually, it would be even faster if you piggybacked me.

512
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:53,200
Hurry up, you have time to speak such nonsense.

513
00:42:53,200 --> 00:42:55,000
It hurts, it hurts.

514
00:42:57,900 --> 00:43:02,700
Then will you wait for me outside when I do the interview later?

515
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:05,930
Do you think I have a lot of time on my hands?

516
00:43:05,930 --> 00:43:08,200
I still need to participate in the competition.

517
00:43:10,180 --> 00:43:13,010
Just when will your foot be better?

518
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:15,600
Soon, soon!

519
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:19,800
Actually, it doesn't seem to hurt that much today.

520
00:43:38,800 --> 00:43:42,990
Hello? Help me look up a phone number.

521
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:45,800
Lin Kaituo.

522
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:53,000
A Little Thing Called First Love

523
00:44:05,500 --> 00:44:08,600
